{"word":"ἐνάρχομαι","slug":"ἐνάρχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐνάρχομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξομαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> in sacrifices, <i>to begin the offering</i>, by taking the barley (<el>οὐλοχύται</el>) from the basket (<el>κανοῦν</el>), <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}